import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { ActivatedRoute } from '@angular/router'; import { UserService } from 'src/app/services/user.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-edit-user', templateUrl: './edit-user.component.html', styleUrls: ['./edit-user.component.css'] }) export class EditUserComponent implements OnInit { constructor(private activatedRoute: ActivatedRoute, private userService: UserService) { } ngOnInit(): void { let username = this.activatedRoute.snapshot.paramMap.get('username') this.getUserByUsername(username); } user = { username: '', password: '', firstName: '', lastName: '', email: '', role: '' } getUserByUsername(username: any) { this.userService.getUserByUsername(username).subscribe((res) => { this.user = res; }) } updateUser() { this.userService.updateUser(this.user).subscribe((res) => { alert("Updated Successfully"); }) } } Edit User
